snippet.title: Fragpunk - Trailer | TGS 2024
snippet.description:
Check out the latest news from Fragpunk, the competitive FPS that blends shooting with card-based powers. Alongside new cards, this TGS trailer also introduces new heroes Sonar and Spider, as well as their unique abilities.
